title: Guitar Books for Dummies (gnv64)
description:
This is a collection of guitar books for dummies. All of them have been uploaded before by various uploaders. I have just brought them together in one torrent. All books are true PDFs with covers:

1. Bass Guitar for Dummies (2nd Ed) by Patrick Pfeiffer (Jan 26, 2010)
  
2. Blues Guitar for Dummies by Jon Chappell (Dec 6, 2006)
  
3. Classical Guitar for Dummies by Jon Chappell and Mark Phillips (Jul 14, 2009)
  
4. Guitar All-in-One for Dummies by Jon Chappell (Aug 3, 2009)
  
5. Guitar Chords for Dummies by Antoine Polin (Jun 21, 2010)
  
6. Guitar Exercises for Dummies by Mark Phillips and Jon Chappell (Dec 10, 2008)
  
7. Guitar For Dummies (2nd Ed)  by Mark Phillips and Jon Chappell (Oct 14, 2005)
